This paper involves analyzing a large dataset of posts on 4chan's /pol/ board, which is a social media platform. Therefore, it is likely to fall under the sub-category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper involves analyzing hate speech and the usage of different types of media, which could fall under the sub-categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the paper involves analyzing the effects of /pol/ on other social media platforms, which could fall under the sub-category of Systems and Control (cs.SD).
